I"4<h1 id="creating-a-blog-and-information-site-for-the-historic-merrit-house-on-orrs-island">Creating a blog and information site for the Historic Merrit House on Orr’s Island.</h1>

<p>1 Purchase Domains merritthouse.info and merritthouse.blog</p>

<p>2 Create new repository on GiHhub ‘merritthouse’</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>* https://rsabec.github.io/merritthouse
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>3 Create A records on DNS</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>* 185.199.108.153
* 185.199.109.153
* 185.199.110.153
* 185.199.111.153
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>4 Created CNAME record on DNS</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>* www CNAME merritthouse.info
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>5 Created Domain Pointer to rsabec.github.io/merritthouse</p>

<p>6 Setup Jekyll site on Github - <a href="http://merritthouse.info/">merritthouse.info</a></p>

